{"tid":568792,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"大學生有咩用？中學大學畢業起薪咪又係 14k！","createTime":"2018-02-22T06:34:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-23T06:58:44.000Z","uid":14170,"like":59,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"2bea676005a4a3e21c2df2140983fbf431930f95","tid":568792,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T06:34:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/22/143337_2195e4891f294c58c22680c1169b0557.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F22%2F143337_2195e4891f294c58c22680c1169b0557.png&h=724017fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/22/143344_101ae3abea262950deadd0aafe645d43.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F22%2F143344_101ae3abea262950deadd0aafe645d43.png&h=e6cc94ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/22/143352_d1daa0152d0d8aaf2cd93c155feb72e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F22%2F143352_d1daa0152d0d8aaf2cd93c155feb72e5.png&h=870f017b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><em><ins>但大學生 30 歲有 30k，中學畢業 30 歲都係 14k </ins></em></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"cddbdf6f00a8f4c0386c05a23d2490b4ffb59f92","tid":568792,"uid":14170,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T06:36:03.000Z","msg":"努力讀書呀各位同學仔，唔好亂信新聞 / 蠢既大人 9up <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f07e1deedb7d1cd3e225353dc4b50a572e2c08c3","tid":568792,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T06:38:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb4b6e9cdd645a69f58faf75f92203bbb9d6304f","tid":568792,"uid":14170,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T06:40:38.000Z","msg":"然而，更為關鍵的問題是，時下年青世代是否仍能隨工作經驗累積而顯著向上 流動。根據二零一六年五月發表的《2015 年收入流動性研究》，主要分析結果 似乎顯示情況較為樂觀。以二零零一/零二年度畢業組羣為例，<strong><em><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不論學位種 類，91%的畢業生</span></ins></span></em></strong>在二零一三/一四年度較在二零零三/零四年度時<ins><em><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">處於較高 的收入十分位數</span></span></strong></em></ins>。至於二零零六/零七年度畢業組羣，逾 80%的畢業生在工 作首五年期間的收入也見向上流動。該研究亦指出，儘管收入向上流動的步伐 主要取決於當時的宏觀經濟環境，但學歷較高的畢業生達到收入分布最高 20%的機會較大。舉例來說，直至二零零四年，香港仍因亞洲金融危機、其後 的經濟下行以至沙士爆發的重大衝擊所帶來的通縮而受到拖累，故此不少二零 零一/零二年度畢業生的入職薪金都十分低。然而，在二零零四至二零零七年 經濟強勁復蘇期間，這些二零零一/零二年度畢業生的收入能夠很快迎頭趕 上，與二零零六/零七年度畢業生相比，最終亦絕不遜色。"},{"pid":"2ff212d9713f004f9762f0de8495552a56fff5ec","tid":568792,"uid":150611,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T07:06:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"142f9ce0ecf8976afb844c752b7aa21257ffaacd","tid":568792,"uid":14094,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T07:06:26.000Z","msg":"重點係 出生年份愈後 人工就愈低<br />\n但通脹唔知多左幾多倍"},{"pid":"f8f7ebfe5dcd13d2770054d9dfc515a46eaa066c","tid":568792,"uid":144843,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T07:09:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c435450ed951212e473f014b572ff7880f21d389","tid":568792,"uid":125258,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"142f9ce0ecf8976afb844c752b7aa21257ffaacd","tid":568792,"uid":14094,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T07:06:26.000Z","msg":"重點係 出生年份愈後 人工就愈低<br />\n但通脹唔知多左幾多倍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T07:17:17.000Z","msg":"錯<br />\n主要既原因係學歷通脹<br />\n阿豬阿狗攞住個top up/學店都話自己大學生<br />\n呢堆人以前計中學畢業，而家就計入大學生group拖低數字<br />\n事實上有睇大學graduate report就知真大學生人工每年仲升緊的"},{"pid":"04ff075f819c30eaec035b2379019d0729864fbd","tid":568792,"uid":134779,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T07:22:10.000Z","msg":"鏗哥系禾偶像🤩<br />\n禾埃尼牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" cl